Our smiles are the light of hope.

00:18:28.315 --> 00:18:30.776
The Holy Mother will appear when we smile.

00:18:31.652 --> 00:18:33.237
So you believe in God.

00:18:38.325 --> 00:18:39.159
Here.

00:18:41.078 --> 00:18:44.081
I've also been doing nothing
but praying recently.

00:18:45.666 --> 00:18:47.000
I don't believe in God.

00:18:48.085 --> 00:18:51.255
But my mother was obsessed
with some cult for a while.

00:18:51.338 --> 00:18:52.381
Hmm.

00:18:54.299 --> 00:18:56.301
Because of that, I was bullied in school.

00:18:56.802 --> 00:18:58.887
But Arisu and Karube saved me.

00:19:01.098 --> 00:19:02.724
They are good friends, aren't they?

00:19:05.060 --> 00:19:08.063
Karube is good at fighting
and the girls really love him,

00:19:08.897 --> 00:19:12.693
and Arisu is so smart
and comes from a respected family.

00:19:13.694 --> 00:19:14.862
Then there's me.

00:19:14.945 --> 00:19:18.031
My family's poor,
and I'm not really good at anything.

00:19:18.991 --> 00:19:23.287
Even now, when I'm hurt and useless,
they're still helping me.

00:19:25.539 --> 00:19:26.707
Some people…

00:19:27.583 --> 00:19:30.043
like being the strongest ones
in their group.

00:19:31.086 --> 00:19:32.546
It makes them feel better.

00:19:34.089 --> 00:19:35.465
They're just so different.

00:19:35.549 --> 00:19:38.260
Think you might feel good enough
to play the next game?

00:19:41.722 --> 00:19:43.015
How does your leg feel?

00:19:46.351 --> 00:19:47.853
They're just so different.

00:19:47.936 --> 00:19:51.356
Are you willing to die too,
to save your friends?

00:20:00.365 --> 00:20:03.535
The game will commence in two minutes.

00:20:04.661 --> 00:20:05.829
Stop following us.

00:20:05.913 --> 00:20:08.290
Just feeling you guys out.

00:20:08.373 --> 00:20:10.626
I'm thinking you two might be
good enough to be my allies.

00:20:10.709 --> 00:20:11.960
Lucky ass.

00:20:12.044 --> 00:20:14.421
- Are you a doctor?
- Nope, real estate agent.

00:20:15.214 --> 00:20:17.049
How many times have you played the game?

00:20:17.132 --> 00:20:19.593
Uh… Let's see, maybe five times?

00:20:20.177 --> 00:20:21.553
And you've always won?

00:20:21.637 --> 00:20:23.388
I guess so, yeah.

00:20:24.473 --> 00:20:26.266
Where should I go to hide?

00:20:26.350 --> 00:20:27.726
Look, I don't know, all right?

00:20:28.227 --> 00:20:29.978
You can only rely on yourself.

00:20:46.745 --> 00:20:48.664
If I wanna see where everyone is,

00:20:49.248 --> 00:20:50.999
this is the perfect location.

00:21:05.597 --> 00:21:06.848
Yeah.

00:21:06.932 --> 00:21:08.976
I got a weird feeling about this.

00:21:16.817 --> 00:21:17.901
Hmm…

00:21:19.027 --> 00:21:21.947
Looks like everyone's about to bite it,
just like they always do.

00:21:23.907 --> 00:21:27.286
I think, maybe
you've always been screwed over, Shibuki.

00:21:27.369 --> 00:21:29.496
You've never met anyone decent.

00:21:31.581 --> 00:21:32.833
You're right.

00:21:38.380 --> 00:21:40.173
Isn't it the same way for you?

00:21:44.678 --> 00:21:46.847
O Holy Mother…

00:21:46.930 --> 00:21:51.101
Please forgive us for all our mortal sins.

00:21:58.066 --> 00:21:59.276
No, you're wrong.

00:22:12.831 --> 00:22:14.249
It must have been rough.

00:22:39.066 --> 00:22:41.651
The game will now commence.

00:22:42.486 --> 00:22:45.739
The time limit is 20 minutes.

00:22:45.822 --> 00:22:47.949
Commence now.

00:22:52.496 --> 00:22:54.915
The tagger is on the move.

00:24:47.152 --> 00:24:49.488
All right,
let's find a room we can get into.

00:24:58.872 --> 00:25:01.458
We gotta get our asses moving!

00:25:20.852 --> 00:25:23.104
Three minutes have passed.

00:25:39.162 --> 00:25:40.539
What the hell was that?

00:26:08.441 --> 00:26:09.359
He's dead.

00:26:36.803 --> 00:26:39.055
Arisu!

00:26:40.056 --> 00:26:41.641
- Run!
- Go, go!

00:26:43.059 --> 00:26:43.893
Arisu!

00:26:43.977 --> 00:26:44.811
- Run!
- Outta the way!

00:26:44.894 --> 00:26:45.937
- Go down!
- Hurry!

00:26:46.021 --> 00:26:47.022
Go, go, go!

00:26:48.607 --> 00:26:49.691
Don't look back! Go!

00:26:50.483 --> 00:26:51.943
Move, move!

00:26:52.027 --> 00:26:54.195
What are you doing? Hey!

00:26:54.904 --> 00:26:56.323
Karube, wait!

00:26:57.032 --> 00:26:58.408
What are you doing?

00:26:59.159 --> 00:27:00.243
Get in there.

00:27:18.428 --> 00:27:20.180
You're a good person, Chota…

00:27:20.847 --> 00:27:22.265
I can trust you, can't I?

00:27:37.322 --> 00:27:38.406
When this started,

00:27:39.949 --> 00:27:41.910
I was having sex with my boss.

00:27:45.205 --> 00:27:46.539
And I hated it.

00:27:48.792 --> 00:27:50.835
I thought you said you were working.

00:27:52.253 --> 00:27:53.922
I don't trust those guys.

00:27:54.673 --> 00:27:56.800
They didn't need to know the truth,
did they?

00:28:19.030 --> 00:28:20.657
Since we're both the same,

00:28:21.533 --> 00:28:22.867
we should work together.

00:28:47.142 --> 00:28:48.601
So we can survive…

00:29:01.906 --> 00:29:03.032
Oh, my god!

00:29:03.116 --> 00:29:05.410
I can't do this. I can't do this!

